00:14:38,632 --> 00:14:40,353
I'm just suggesting that as a weird thing.

274
00:14:41,494 --> 00:14:42,994
There's no necklace of human fingers in this game.

275
00:14:43,575 --> 00:14:45,816
Furthermore, I googled that to put it into the talk,

276
00:14:46,136 --> 00:14:48,997
and then I realized that if I showed people what I found,

277
00:14:49,157 --> 00:14:50,658
somebody would be sick and barf.

