00:21:18,257 --> 00:21:19,038
It's level design.

406
00:21:19,538 --> 00:21:20,219
It's programming.

407
00:21:20,759 --> 00:21:26,465
It's the most disciplinary, multidisciplinary thing that you can do, I think, at times.

408
00:21:26,985 --> 00:21:32,310
And in my day-to-day, game writing is actually systems design plus tools development plus

409
00:21:32,330 --> 00:21:32,851
creative direction.

